<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671944' id='t-671944'>and we have to protect it now
because our online data</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674777' id='t-674777'>is more than just a collection
of ones and zeros.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677541' id='t-677541'>It's actually a lot more than that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679397' id='t-679397'>It's our lives, our personal stories,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='681743' id='t-681743'>our friends, our families,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684041' id='t-684041'>and in many ways,
also our hopes and our aspirations.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='687547' id='t-687547'>We need to spend time now
to really protect our right</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690651' id='t-690651'>to share this only with people
