<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696341' id='t-696341'>So now's the time for us
to collectively stand up and say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699194' id='t-699194'>yes, we do want to live
in a world with online privacy,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702687' id='t-702687'>and yes, we can work together
to turn this vision into a reality.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707215' id='t-707215'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:00
